WEBVTT

00:07.702 --> 00:10.100
<i>Previously on "Billions"...</i>

00:10.125 --> 00:13.209
So, the key to bagging Axe is...?

00:13.264 --> 00:14.131
[Bryan] <i> Pete Decker.</i>

00:14.217 --> 00:17.777
Mr. Decker, we have an
awful lot to talk about.

00:17.829 --> 00:19.712
[Tara] <i> You think you're
gonna fucking blackmail me?</i>

00:19.747 --> 00:23.449
You're gonna watch, listen, and report.

00:23.451 --> 00:26.118
We got a subpoena on your
folks' investment portfolio,

00:26.170 --> 00:28.721
and it seems that they were
in on the Pepsum trade.

00:28.756 --> 00:30.172
Yeah, I'll come in on Monday.

00:30.208 --> 00:32.558
I just lost my mojo
somewhere along the line.

00:32.593 --> 00:33.631
[Mick] It's fucking gone.

00:33.743 --> 00:35.764
Everyone else is up double digits.

00:37.178 --> 00:38.130
I'm down.

00:38.132 --> 00:39.799
You're just listening to the wrong voice.

00:39.801 --> 00:41.780
It's what I like to call
the prisoner's dilemma.

00:41.811 --> 00:43.969
No, you don't like to call it that.
That's what it's called.

00:44.021 --> 00:46.108
[Chuck] Does no one ever
check you on this bullshit?

00:46.192 --> 00:48.428
You have to ask yourself,

00:49.277 --> 00:51.544
"What is he gonna attack next?"

00:51.579 --> 00:55.194
Find a way to bury the son of a bitch.

00:55.221 --> 00:57.221
I haven't been able to get
Garth Sykes on the phone.

00:57.318 --> 00:58.751
He bails, it hurts us.

00:58.786 --> 01:01.487
When can I see Axe and
talk to him about it?

01:01.539 --> 01:03.222
It's a crush-the-other-guy business.

01:03.257 --> 01:04.811
[Bobby] It's like <i> Highlander.</i>

01:04.863 --> 01:06.295
There can be only one.

01:07.600 --> 01:09.702
I want to give you a short
that you're not gonna bail on.

01:09.756 --> 01:10.713
[Bobby] Do you know Cross-Co.?

01:10.748 --> 01:12.498
I don't see the short play.

01:12.928 --> 01:15.668
I don't need you to see it.
I need you to <i> do</i> it.

