♪<i> In the salsify mains of
what was thought but unsaid</i> ♪

55:19.295 --> 55:23.964
♪<i> All the calcified arithmatists
were doing the math</i> ♪

55:25.884 --> 55:29.303
♪<i> And it would take a
calculated blow to the head</i> ♪

55:29.355 --> 55:34.107
♪<i> To light the eyes of all
the harmless sociopaths</i> ♪

55:35.978 --> 55:39.413
♪<i> Oh, arm in arm, we are
the harmless sociopaths</i> ♪

